<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>252</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zǒu guò huáng tǔ gāo pō yě zǒu guò jiāng nán shuǐ xiāng
 zǒu guò fán huá de dōu shì yě zǒu guò piān pì de cūn zhuāng
 zuì nán wàng de shì bù gāo de ǎi qiáng hái yǒu chái mén zài fēng zhōng zhī zhī xiǎng
 nà lǐ yǒu wǒ dì xiōng hé jiě mèi xiàn zài shì fǒu ān rán wú yàng
 wǒ zhù fú nǐ zǒu guò de de fāng bié wàng jì kàn gù qún yáng
 gěi yóu zi pù yī tiáo huí jiā de lù chéng wèi hēi yè lǐ de liàng guāng.</lyrics>
<title>zǒu guò huáng tǔ gāo pō 迦南252</title>
</song>